OL,5, The boss of P&O Ferries Peter          
OL,6, Hebblethwaite is facing mounting       
OL,7, pressure to resign over the no-notice  
OL,8, sackings of 800 staff.                 
OL,10,FTransport Secretary Grant Shapps called
OL,11,Ffor him to step down after his "brazen"
OL,12,Fand "breathtaking" law breaking.       
OL,14,FMr Hebblethwaite admitted to MPs that  
OL,15,Fhe broke the law by not consulting     
OL,16,Fworkers but said he would make the same
OL,17,Fdecision again if he had to.           
OL,19,FThe transport committee chairman has   
OL,20,Falso called for Mr Hebblethwaite to go.
